name: Disney by Loungefly Backpack Sleeping Beauty Lenticular Princess Series
description:
Dream up enchanting adventures with our Loungefly Disney Sleeping Beauty Princess Lenticular Mini Backpack. Disney's Aurora graces the front, and she looks into a window, which reveals her future: she and Prince Phillip are dancing! Lenticular details, though, offer an alternate view in which she pricks her finger on the spindle of a spinning wheel, thus fulfilling Maleficent's curse. Debossed flowers and woodland creatures frame the window, and a diagonal zipper behind Aurora's pink flowing dress allows you to secure smaller items for all your journeys. On the side pockets, you'll find the Good Fairies (Merryweather, Flora, and Fauna) and a woodland squirrel with flowers. Aurora and Prince Phillip dance together in an encore appearance on the back. Make a dreamy entrance wherever you go with this stylish vision of a backpack. The Loungefly Disney Sleeping Beauty Princess Lenticular Mini Backpack is made of vegan leather (polyurethane). Bag has adjustable shoulder straps, side pockets, and shiny gold-colored metal hardware. Additional features include applique, lenticular, debossed, and printed details. Take note of the coordinating inside lining. This backpack is an officially licensed Disney product. Backpack dimensions: 9"W x 10.5"H x 4.5"D


Material: Polyester / Faux Leather
Size: 23 x 25 x 11 cm
